work.summary: Founded Kona Kruzers LLC, which provides vacation rental RVs to tourists visiting Oahu. Dedicated time and capital to start and continue to grow the business. Initially responsible for all marketing and client contact, then hired employees to expand the business further.

Worked with credit analysts and underwriters in helping to produce credit analysis documents on commercial loans. Gained exposure to the commercial credit issuance process from request to approval. Worked on commercial real-estate deals and appraisals, and participated in commercial business client calls.

Used Jira issue tracking software to provide feedback to project managers in developing digital banking software. Duties included performing and reporting on Digital Banking product tests in support of product development.
